    7,                       !- Begin Month
    21,                      !- Begin Day of Month
    7,                       !- End Month
    21,                      !- End Day of Month
    Monday,                  !- Day of Week for Start Day
    Yes,                     !- Use Weather File Daylight Saving Period
    Yes;                     !- Use Weather File Rain and Snow Indicators

